reviews.reviewText: Not only did they fit where I needed them to, the quality of the tissues are great and I’m proud to show the box sayings. You nailed it! Thank you!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 3, 2024
reviews.reviewText: I gave this out as gifts to my catechists. Yes, Joshua is spelled incorrectly on 3. I took a thin marker & turned JOSHUR into JOSHUA.. Problem solved. ☺️Tissues feel ok, but it’s refillable so I will use a better quality when it runs out.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 23, 2023
reviews.reviewText: Great gift but buyer beware Joshua is misspelled to Joshur . I thought it was just mine but I came back to here and check the photo description and it also is misspelled. EXTREMELY disappointing. The packaging was also not so great. These were packaged so tight that some of the tissue cylinders were damaged and some were open. I really like these but will not be ordering again.
